# Breadcrumb

Version: 1.0

Author: [Fumito Mizuno](http://twitter.com/ounziw)

Lastupdate outputs a list of recently updated pages.

##Installation

Copy the addon in a folder named 'lastupdate' in system/mojomotor/third_party

##Usage

Lastupdate has a function:

    {mojo:lastupdate:create}

simply returns a list of the recently updated page.

Optionally, you can set the number of pages shown in the list.

    {mojo:lastupdate:create number="5"}

returns the list of the five recently updated pages.

The parameter 'number' must be a positive integer.

Date format will be set in the view, though I'm not sure it is a good way.

